A simple AI-powered chatbot using OpenAI GPT.

## Installation
1. Clone this repository

git clone https://github.com/kwadoezza/AI-Portfolio.git

2. Install dependencies:

pip install -r requirements.txt

3. Run the chatbot:

python chatbot.py

## Features:
- Uses OpenAI API for generating responses
- Simple command-line interface
